    Support flatten with axis = 0 (#5843)

    Summary:
    Pull Request resolved: https://github.com/pytorch/glow/pull/5843

    The current implementation of flatten assumes by default axis >= 1. When checking caffe2/nnpi compatibility, a number of tests use axis=0 with flattening, which should flatten the shape to {1, num elements}

    Reviewed By: khabinov

    Differential Revision: D31652784

    fbshipit-source-id: d3f1339e5709afa9043d9f64bfb76fea31294e87
---
 lib/Graph/Graph.cpp | 11 ++++++++++-
