    Fix the isInput logic (#5720)

    Summary:
    Pull Request resolved: https://github.com/pytorch/glow/pull/5720

    Take into account the order of instructions using a given buffer. If the first use is a write, this buffer is not an input.

    Reviewed By: SameerAsal, chenccfb

